text: Dandot (ڈنڈوت) is a village and Union Council, an administrative subdivision, of Chakwal District in the Punjab Province of Pakistan, it is part of Choa Saidan Shah Tehsil and is located at 32°39'0N 72°58'0ELocation of Dandot - Falling Rain Genomics ==References== Category:Union councils of Chakwal District
